{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, we aimed to systematically assess the capability of GPT-4 to generate pathological diagnoses from images across various organs, including colon biopsies.",
    "By comparing the performance of GPT-4 with that of different experienced pathologists, we sought to highlight both the strengths and limitations of this AI model in a diagnostic context.",
    "Understanding GPT-4's proficiency in interpreting and analyzing pathology images is essential to assess its potential as a valuable tool for supporting pathologists and enhancing diagnostic workflows.",
    "This study included two distinct datasets.",
    "Dataset A consisted of 44 images sourced from 16 different organ systems, most of which were obtained from publicly available web photographs."
  ]
}